<c.bg_transparent>Si el viento nos acompaña,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>¿podemos cruzar la bahía rápido?</c.bg_transparent>

107
00:08:39.227 --> 00:08:41.103 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Sí, claro!</c.bg_transparent>

108
00:08:41.354 --> 00:08:42.939 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Habrá una tormenta.</c.bg_transparent>

109
00:08:43.022 --> 00:08:45.691 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Una tormenta? Qué interesante.</c.bg_transparent>

110
00:08:45.983 --> 00:08:48.694 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Así que debemos posponer la salida.</c.bg_transparent>

111
00:08:48.903 --> 00:08:51.030 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tenemos un cronograma ajustado.</c.bg_transparent>

112
00:08:51.113 --> 00:08:53.199 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿No hay nada que podamos hacer?</c.bg_transparent>

113
00:08:54.242 --> 00:08:58.371 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Si partimos ya mismo,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>podríamos ganarle a la tormenta.</c.bg_transparent>

114
00:08:58.454 --> 00:08:59.705 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hagamos eso.</c.bg_transparent>

115
00:09:00.248 --> 00:09:01.207 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Perfecto!</c.bg_transparent>

116
00:09:01.582 --> 00:09:05.044 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A menos que la tormenta nos alcance</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>en el medio y nos mate.</c.bg_transparent>

117
00:09:15.638 --> 00:09:18.140 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Se preguntarán qué me pasó en los ojos.</c.bg_transparent>

118
00:09:18.432 --> 00:09:20.434 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No quería ser grosero.</c.bg_transparent>

119
00:09:20.726 --> 00:09:23.854 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>El izquierdo me lo quitó</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>una bandada de gaviotas.</c.bg_transparent>

120
00:09:25.565 --> 00:09:26.816 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Y el derecho?</c.bg_transparent>

121
00:09:27.149 --> 00:09:29.610 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No sé, la amenaza llegó de la izquierda.</c.bg_transparent>

122
00:09:37.118 --> 00:09:41.622 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Cómo vamos hacia allí</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>si el viento sopla hacia allá?</c.bg_transparent>

123
00:09:42.623 --> 00:09:44.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Así se navega, joven.</c.bg_transparent>

124
00:09:45.334 --> 00:09:47.628 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿El viento no nos empuja</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a donde vamos?</c.bg_transparent>

125
00:09:48.004 --> 00:09:51.424 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>La vela es como un ala,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>vuela a través del viento</c.bg_transparent>

126
00:09:51.507 --> 00:09:54.343 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>empujando el barco</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>contra las corrientes debajo.</c.bg_transparent>

127
00:09:54.719 --> 00:09:58.556 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Es como lanzar una semilla</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>de entre los dedos.</c.bg_transparent>

128
00:09:59.015 --> 00:10:02.727 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>La aprietas de ambos lados,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>y sale disparada hacia delante.</c.bg_transparent>

129
00:10:05.146 --> 00:10:06.314 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Creo que entiendo.</c.bg_transparent>

130
00:10:10.401 --> 00:10:12.737 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tras un tiempo en los elementos,</c.bg_transparent>

131
00:10:12.820 --> 00:10:16.741 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>percibes dónde está el viento</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>y cómo cambiará.</c.bg_transparent>

132
00:10:16.824 --> 00:10:19.118 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Es como una conexión</c.bg_transparent>

133
00:10:19.327 --> 00:10:20.745 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>profunda en tu ser.</c.bg_transparent>

134
00:10:20.828 --> 00:10:23.456 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Siente una conexión con el viento?</c.bg_transparent>

135
00:10:23.539 --> 00:10:25.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>- ¿Cómo la logró?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- ¿Qué?</c.bg_transparent>

136
00:10:25.625 --> 00:10:29.462 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Por ser ciego y narcoléptico</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>no puedo navegar?</c.bg_transparent>

137
00:10:29.545 --> 00:10:32.340 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No quise decir eso. ¿Narcoléptico?</c.bg_transparent>

138
00:10:34.383 --> 00:10:37.637 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Despiértate!</c.bg_transparent>

139
00:10:37.720 --> 00:10:39.096 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Qué pasó?</c.bg_transparent>

140
00:10:39.263 --> 00:10:42.808 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Recuerdo que hablaba de narcolepsia</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>y me dormí.</c.bg_transparent>

141
00:10:43.142 --> 00:10:44.810 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sí, exacto.</c.bg_transparent>

142
00:10:53.194 --> 00:10:56.947 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Se aproxima la tormenta.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Al final, no le ganaremos.</c.bg_transparent>

143
00:10:59.533 --> 00:11:01.994 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>- Es mi oportunidad.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- De morir.</c.bg_transparent>

144
00:11:02.078 --> 00:11:04.455 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Iba a decir: "De aprender".</c.bg_transparent>

145
00:11:04.789 --> 00:11:06.457 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡A ahogarte!</c.bg_transparent>

146
00:11:40.574 --> 00:11:43.202 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Jamás había visto esta runa.</c.bg_transparent>

147
00:12:17.319 --> 00:12:19.113 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Pretendes que beba esto?</c.bg_transparent>

148
00:12:30.791 --> 00:12:32.835 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No es tan terrible.</c.bg_transparent>

149
00:12:48.434 --> 00:12:51.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Por qué confiaría en ti? Ni sé quién...</c.bg_transparent>

150
00:12:51.604 --> 00:12:53.606 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Ni siquiera sé qué eres!</c.bg_transparent>

151
00:12:58.402 --> 00:12:59.737 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Necesito pensar.</c.bg_transparent>

152
00:13:12.124 --> 00:13:13.834 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Estás cambiando de color.</c.bg_transparent>

153
00:13:13.918 --> 00:13:15.544 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Esa es tu forma lunar?</c.bg_transparent>

154
00:13:15.628 --> 00:13:19.131 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, es mi imitación del sapo luminoso.</c.bg_transparent>

155
00:13:25.054 --> 00:13:26.597 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>La tormenta es muy fuerte.</c.bg_transparent>

156
00:13:26.680 --> 00:13:30.601 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Será mejor atracar a sotavento de la isla</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>hasta que se calme.</c.bg_transparent>

157
00:13:33.020 --> 00:13:34.772 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Berto, ¡a proa!</c.bg_transparent>

158
00:13:36.607 --> 00:13:39.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Sí! ¡A babor!</c.bg_transparent>

159
00:13:49.870 --> 00:13:51.914 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Suelten las velas!</c.bg_transparent>

160
00:13:58.587 --> 00:14:00.172 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡A estribor!</c.bg_transparent>

161
00:14:10.558 --> 00:14:11.934 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡A babor!</c.bg_transparent>

162
00:14:25.155 --> 00:14:26.991 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Lo logramos! ¡Graznido!</c.bg_transparent>

163
00:14:28.117 --> 00:14:30.202 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Acaba de decir "graznido"?</c.bg_transparent>

164
00:15:06.655 --> 00:15:07.990 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No entiendo.</c.bg_transparent>

165
00:15:08.240 --> 00:15:10.367 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Por qué abandonarían el puesto?</c.bg_transparent>

166
00:15:10.451 --> 00:15:12.369 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Recién enviaron la señal...</c.bg_transparent>

167
00:15:15.873 --> 00:15:18.167 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Soldado, envió tarde la señal.</c.bg_transparent>

168
00:15:18.250 --> 00:15:20.127 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Qué pasó? ¿Y los demás?</c.bg_transparent>

169
00:15:20.210 --> 00:15:22.087 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sí, disculpe, señor.</c.bg_transparent>

170
00:15:22.171 --> 00:15:24.882 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Los demás se fueron a patrullar</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>y se me pasó.</c.bg_transparent>

171
00:15:24.965 --> 00:15:27.301 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>La próxima señal será puntual.</c.bg_transparent>

172
00:16:10.886 --> 00:16:12.972 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No le ganamos a la tormenta.</c.bg_transparent>

173
00:16:13.263 --> 00:16:15.391 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Habrá que esperar bajo cubierta.</c.bg_transparent>

174
00:16:15.474 --> 00:16:19.103 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Genial, estamos mojados</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>y no avanzamos nada.</c.bg_transparent>

175
00:16:21.730 --> 00:16:24.024 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oye, ¿no vienes?</c.bg_transparent>

176
00:16:25.067 --> 00:16:26.443 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sí. Tienes razón.</c.bg_transparent>

177
00:16:29.279 --> 00:16:30.739 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Conozco esa expresión.</c.bg_transparent>

178
00:16:30.823 --> 00:16:33.283 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Es la expresión de idea tonta.</c.bg_transparent>

179
00:16:35.828 --> 00:16:37.830 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Cada vez que cae un rayo,</c.bg_transparent>

180
00:16:37.913 --> 00:16:39.206 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>siento algo.</c.bg_transparent>

181
00:16:39.790 --> 00:16:41.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sí, yo también.</c.bg_transparent>

182
00:16:41.417 --> 00:16:44.420 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Se siente bien que no te caiga el rayo.</c.bg_transparent>

183
00:16:44.503 --> 00:16:48.298 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, me siento igual</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>que con el hechizo Fulminis.</c.bg_transparent>

184
00:16:48.841 --> 00:16:53.512 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quizás si soy valiente</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>y enfrento la tormenta,</c.bg_transparent>

185
00:16:53.595 --> 00:16:55.097 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>conseguiré una conexión.</c.bg_transparent>

186
00:16:55.347 --> 00:16:57.141 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>O terminarás muerto.</c.bg_transparent>

187
00:17:02.479 --> 00:17:04.273 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Ves? Zym lo entiende.</c.bg_transparent>

188
00:17:04.481 --> 00:17:05.899 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Él también lo siente.</c.bg_transparent>

189
00:17:07.443 --> 00:17:09.820 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quieres ir, ¿no?</c.bg_transparent>

190
00:17:10.320 --> 00:17:11.822 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, no.</c.bg_transparent>

191
00:17:11.905 --> 00:17:15.409 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Una cosa es que arriesgues tu vida humana,</c.bg_transparent>

192
00:17:15.492 --> 00:17:19.538 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>no dejaré que arriesgues la vida</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>del futuro rey de los dragones.</c.bg_transparent>

193
00:17:22.124 --> 00:17:23.751 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Es un dragón fuerte.</c.bg_transparent>

194
00:17:25.210 --> 00:17:26.253 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Estará a salvo.</c.bg_transparent>

195
00:17:31.091 --> 00:17:32.426 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Si mueres ahí,</c.bg_transparent>

196
00:17:32.509 --> 00:17:34.178 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>juro que te mataré.</c.bg_transparent>

197
00:17:40.267 --> 00:17:41.185 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Muy bien.</c.bg_transparent>

198
00:17:41.769 --> 00:17:42.770 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Llueve.</c.bg_transparent>

199
00:17:44.772 --> 00:17:46.106 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>El viento sopla.</c.bg_transparent>

200
00:17:47.524 --> 00:17:48.817 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sopla muchísimo.</c.bg_transparent>

201
00:17:49.443 --> 00:17:50.486 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tengo frío.</c.bg_transparent>

202
00:17:51.111 --> 00:17:52.279 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Estoy empapado.</c.bg_transparent>

203
00:17:52.529 --> 00:17:56.575 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿La piel debe arrugarse así</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>cuando entiendes el arcano celeste?</c.bg_transparent>

204
00:18:00.120 --> 00:18:02.206 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No me siento distinto.</c.bg_transparent>

205
00:18:06.376 --> 00:18:08.337 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quizá debo ir más arriba.</c.bg_transparent>

206
00:18:36.073 --> 00:18:38.408 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No sé cómo hacerlo, Zym.</c.bg_transparent>

207
00:18:38.742 --> 00:18:41.703 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tú eres una criatura mágica.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Lo tienes en ti.</c.bg_transparent>

208
00:18:41.829 --> 00:18:43.831 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pero yo soy humano.</c.bg_transparent>

209
00:18:43.914 --> 00:18:45.624 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No tengo nada adentro.</c.bg_transparent>

210
00:18:46.416 --> 00:18:47.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Deseo tanto esto.</c.bg_transparent>

211
00:18:48.335 --> 00:18:51.505 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Cuando hice magia, me sentí yo mismo</c.bg_transparent>

212
00:18:51.588 --> 00:18:53.882 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>y ahora lo perdí.</c.bg_transparent>

213
00:18:54.508 --> 00:18:56.343 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quiero reencaminarme.</c.bg_transparent>

214
00:19:03.517 --> 00:19:05.561 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Parece la roca primaria.</c.bg_transparent>

215
00:19:05.644 --> 00:19:07.271 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Ahí necesitamos ir!</c.bg_transparent>

216
00:19:25.205 --> 00:19:26.623 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Me llegó un mensaje?</c.bg_transparent>

217
00:19:26.707 --> 00:19:29.293 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Sí! De hecho, cuatro.</c.bg_transparent>

218
00:19:29.376 --> 00:19:32.212 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Recibí cuatro mensajes</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>y no me informaron?</c.bg_transparent>

219
00:19:32.296 --> 00:19:34.715 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lo buscamos por todo el castillo.</c.bg_transparent>

220
00:19:34.798 --> 00:19:36.300 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No lo encontramos.</c.bg_transparent>

221
00:19:36.383 --> 00:19:39.928 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Se esconde en algún cuarto secreto?</c.bg_transparent>

222
00:19:40.762 --> 00:19:42.306 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Estaba en el baño.</c.bg_transparent>

223
00:19:43.348 --> 00:19:44.641 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Claro.</c.bg_transparent>

224
00:19:51.773 --> 00:19:55.027 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Los demás reinos aceptaron</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>la cumbre de la pentarquía.</c.bg_transparent>

225
00:19:55.110 --> 00:19:56.945 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Eso parece importante.</c.bg_transparent>

226
00:19:57.613 --> 00:20:00.657 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Reuniré a los reyes y a las reinas,</c.bg_transparent>

227
00:20:00.741 --> 00:20:03.076 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡y destruiré la amenaza de Xadia!</c.bg_transparent>

228
00:20:04.244 --> 00:20:06.622 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Eres testigo de un hecho histórico.</c.bg_transparent>

229
00:20:07.623 --> 00:20:08.957 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Genial.</c.bg_transparent>

230
00:20:09.541 --> 00:20:13.045 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Calificaría la atención que recibió hoy</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>como "excelente"?</c.bg_transparent>

231
00:20:22.012 --> 00:20:23.472 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Es un pararrayos.</c.bg_transparent>

232
00:20:40.030 --> 00:20:41.281 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tal vez si...</c.bg_transparent>

233
00:20:44.952 --> 00:20:45.994 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, no puedo.</c.bg_transparent>

234
00:20:48.205 --> 00:20:49.414 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Debo hacerlo.</c.bg_transparent>

235
00:20:49.498 --> 00:20:51.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Debo entender la fuente celeste.</c.bg_transparent>

236
00:20:57.422 --> 00:20:58.924 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Vamos!</c.bg_transparent>

237
00:21:07.224 --> 00:21:09.017 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Callum, eres un idiota.</c.bg_transparent>

238
00:21:09.351 --> 00:21:12.896 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No puedes arriesgar tu vida</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>para aprender magia.</c.bg_transparent>

239
00:21:12.980 --> 00:21:14.064 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Es una locura.</c.bg_transparent>

240
00:23:22.025 --> 00:23:23.652 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Callum! ¿Qué pasó?</c.bg_transparent>

241
00:23:25.028 --> 00:23:27.823 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Fuimos al corazón de la tormenta,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>y a Zym...</c.bg_transparent>

242
00:23:28.615 --> 00:23:30.242 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>...le cayó un rayo.</c.bg_transparent>

243
00:23:34.162 --> 00:23:35.497 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Creo que está bien.</c.bg_transparent>

244
00:23:40.585 --> 00:23:41.545 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Qué ocurre?</c.bg_transparent>

245
00:23:42.254 --> 00:23:44.923 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Soy un tonto. Tenías razón.</c.bg_transparent>

246
00:23:45.048 --> 00:23:46.007 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Callum...</c.bg_transparent>

247
00:23:47.592 --> 00:23:49.302 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Casi hago que Zym muera.</c.bg_transparent>

248
00:23:49.428 --> 00:23:51.263 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nos puse en peligro.</c.bg_transparent>

249
00:23:51.430 --> 00:23:55.350 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Y cuando estábamos</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>en el medio de la tormenta...</c.bg_transparent>

250
00:23:55.434 --> 00:23:58.687 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Creí que realmente quería esto,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>pero, al final...</c.bg_transparent>

251
00:23:58.937 --> 00:24:00.522 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>...no me animé.</c.bg_transparent>

252
00:24:02.774 --> 00:24:03.608 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Qué bueno.</c.bg_transparent>

253
00:25:27.609 --> 00:25:29.528 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
